MsgQueueConsumerRunnable - Class in com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.runnables
Represents a Runnable instance of the MsgQueue Consumer thread This class basically tries to get a lock on the InternalMsgQueue and convert the Message instance to the InternalMessage instance and add it to the InternalMsgQueue If it is unable to get a Lock on the InternalMsgQueue, it does not block the MsgQueue, but waits for some specified milliseconds (50ms) on the MsgQueue, after which it tries again.
Thus this incurs minimum wait on the publishers trying to add the message to the MsgQueue
